Nineteen61

A Culinary delight
Nineteen61, a recognized premier fine dining destination in Florida was brought to life by owner and lead Chef, Marcos Fernandez. The menu is full of memorable items that combine a modern Spanish style accompanied by a Latin American twist with a Southern propensity.
At Nineteen61, we position ourselves as a benchmark for Lakeland dining. A new standard that shows what is possible—what Lakeland diners should expect from their restaurants. Despite it all, including our humbling success, it has never been about monetary success. It is not about recognition or press. Instead, it is about the food, the freedom, and sharing these bounties with a community we love.
With a focus on quality and creating an in-depth memorable experience beyond a crafted dish, the wine poured in your glass and linens on your table- we believe it requires more than just that.
“In the heart of our culinary journey lies Nineteen61, a restaurant that emerged from humble beginnings, where passion ignited the flame of creativity. “

Nineteen61

EVENT CATERING SERVICES
Welcome to Events at Nineteen61, where we deliver exceptional culinary experiences tailored to your event's unique style. Whether you need onsite catering with live-action stations or offsite catering at a venue of your choice, we have the expertise to make your event unforgettable. We specialize in Cuban, Italian, and American cuisine, offering a variety of delectable dishes to suit all tastes. Our services also include in-house bakery made dessert items and custom floral and décor services, ensuring your celebration is flawless from start to finish.
CREATING MEMORABLE MOMENTS
Our expert planning team ensures a seamless event experience from concept to completion.
• Themed Décor:
Tablescapes, Floral Arrangements, and Centerpieces
• Event Coordination:
Timelines, Vendor Management, and Logistics
Onsite Catering
• Perfect for corporate events, weddings, and private parties at our exclusive venues, featuring seated dining up to 90 guests.
• Cocktail and Tapas service for 100 or more guests.
• Live chef stations, buffet setups, and plated meals available.
Offsite Catering
• We bring the feast to your location—whether it's a poolside wedding, corporate office, or family reunion.
• Full-service staff to set up, serve, and clean up.
Cuban Cuisine
Experience the vibrant flavors of Cuba with a menu full of soulful, slow-cooked dishes.
Sample Menu Items:
•
Appetizers:
House made tapas including Tostones with Aji Panca marinated pork,
Croquetas with Serrano ham and bechamel, Empanadas featuring sweet and savory
seasoned beef with olives & raisins, Rocoto sauce
• Entrées:
Ropa Vieja (Shredded Beef Stew), Lechón Asado (Cuban Roast Pork), Whole Pig
Roast, Paella and so much more
• Sides:
Black Beans & Jasmine Rice, Yuca con Mojo
• Desserts:
Guava Cheesecake, Tres Leches Cake, Specialty Tarts and more
ITALIAN Cuisine
Savor the comfort of authentic Italian food made with love and tradition.
Sample Menu Items:
• Appetizers:
Caprese Salad Skewers, Bruschetta al Pomodoro
• Entrées:
Chicken Marsala, Rigatoni61, Pasta Primavera, Eggplant Parmesan
• Sides:
Garlic Bread Sticks, Caesar Salad
• Desserts:
Tiramisu, Cannoli
AMERICAN Cuisine
Classic American favorites, reimagined with fresh ingredients and creative flair.
Sample Menu Items:
• Appetizers:
Mini Pork Sliders, BBQ Chicken Wings, Deviled Eggs
• Entrées:
Shrimp and Grits, Grilled and Sliced Steak, Southern Fried Chicken
• Sides:
Mac & Cheese, Coleslaw, Cornbread
• Desserts:
Apple Pie, Cheesecake, Brownies
Request Info
Whether it’s an intimate gathering or a grand celebration, we are committed to delivering an unforgettable event. Contact us today to discuss your vision and let us create an extraordinary experience for you and your guests!
